label: Phaleron Bioarchaeological Project age estimation dataset section
definition: A section of an age-estimation dataset created for and by the Phaleron Bioarchaeological Project.

label: Suchey-Brooks dataset section
definition: Section of a Phaleron Bioarchaeological Project age-estimation dataset that contains information about an investigation following the Suchey-Brooks method.

label: Age estimation dataset
definition: A dataset that contains information from one investigation estimating age at death according to the methods set forth by the Phaleron Bioarchaeological Project.
